  "text": "# FxVanillaOption Type Family Lineage - Complete Trace\n\n## Overview\nThe FxVanillaOption type family in OpenGamma Strata is a comprehensive type hierarchy for modeling and pricing foreign exchange vanilla options. The type family spans across four core modules (product, pricer, measure, loader) with a specialized barrier option variant that embeds FxVanillaOption.\n\n## 1. Core Joda-Beans Domain Classes (modules/product/)\n\nThe foundation of the type family consists of four core Joda-Beans domain classes located in `com.opengamma.strata.product.fxopt` package:\n\n### Unresolved (Market-facing) Types:\n- **FxVanillaOption** (`modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxVanillaOption.java`): The core domain model representing an FX vanilla option with strike, expiry, and underlying FX transaction details.\n- **FxVanillaOptionTrade** (`modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTrade.java`): Wraps FxVanillaOption with trade metadata (counterparty, settlement, premium, trade info).\n\n### Resolved (Calculation-ready) Types:\n- **ResolvedFxVanillaOption** (`modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/ResolvedFxVanillaOption.java`): Resolved version of FxVanillaOption with fixed dates and rates after reference data resolution.\n- **ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade** (`modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade.java`): Trade-level resolved version combining resolved option with payment details.\n\n## 2. Pricer Classes (modules/pricer/)\n\nThe pricer module (`com.opengamma.strata.pricer.fxopt` package) contains four pricer implementations supporting two valuation methodologies (Black and Vanna-Volga), each with product-level and trade-level pricers:\n\n### Black Model (Lognormal Model):\n- **BlackFxVanillaOptionProductPricer** (`modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/BlackFxVanillaOptionProductPricer.java`): Prices ResolvedFxVanillaOption products using Black's formula for lognormal distributions.\n- **BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer** (`modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer.java`): Prices ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade (product + premium payments) using Black model.\n\n### Vanna-Volga Model (Smile Adjustment):\n- **VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionProductPricer** (`modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionProductPricer.java`): Implements Vanna-Volga method for pricing with volatility smile adjustments using three market points (ATM, 10-delta call, 10-delta put).\n- **VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer** (`modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer.java`): Trade-level pricer extending Vanna-Volga product pricing to include premium payments.\n\nBoth product and trade pricers calculate PV (present value), delta, gamma, vega, and theta sensitivities.\n\n## 3. Measure Calculation Classes (modules/measure/)\n\nThe measure module (`com.opengamma.strata.measure.fxopt` package) provides the calculation engine integration layer with four classes wiring pricers to the scenario calculation framework:\n\n- **FxVanillaOptionMethod** (`modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionMethod.java`): Enum implementing CalculationParameter to select between Black and Vanna-Volga pricing methods.\n- **FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations** (`modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations.java`): Core calculations class that executes pricing and risk measures (PV, delta, gamma, vega, theta, bucketed sensitivities) using either Black or Vanna-Volga pricers based on the selected method and market data.\n- **FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction** (`modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction.java`): Implements CalculationFunction to integrate FxVanillaOptionTrade pricing into Strata's calculation framework, handling requirement analysis and scenario market data lookup.\n- **FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculations** (`modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculations.java`): High-level API providing direct calculation methods for trades using the selected pricing method, internally delegating to pricers.\n\n## 4. Data Loader Integration (modules/loader/)\n\n- **FxVanillaOptionTradeCsvPlugin** (`modules/loader/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/loader/csv/FxVanillaOptionTradeCsvPlugin.java`): CSV data loader plugin for parsing FX vanilla option trades from CSV format, handling columns for expiry dates/times, strikes, notionals, currencies, premiums, and payment dates. Implements the plugin interface for dynamic registration in the CSV loader registry.\n\n## 5. Related Type: FxSingleBarrierOption (Embedded Dependency)\n\n- **FxSingleBarrierOption** (`modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxSingleBarrierOption.java`): A barrier variant option that embeds FxVanillaOption as its core dependency (property: `underlyingOption`). This composition allows barrier knock-in/knock-out variants to wrap vanilla options with barrier conditions and optional rebates. FxSingleBarrierOption implements Resolvable and resolves to ResolvedFxSingleBarrierOption by invoking the underlying vanilla option's resolve method.\n\n## Type Hierarchy Summary\n\n```\nFxVanillaOption (core product)\n├─ wrapped by: FxVanillaOptionTrade (with trade info)\n├─ resolves to: ResolvedFxVanillaOption\n│  └─ wrapped by: ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade\n├─ priced by (product level):\n│  ├─ BlackFxVanillaOptionProductPricer\n│  └─ VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionProductPricer\n├─ priced by (trade level):\n│  ├─ BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer\n│  └─ VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer\n├─ calculated by (measures):\n│  ├─ FxVanillaOptionMethod (method selection)\n│  ├─ FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations (core calcs)\n│  ├─ FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction (framework integration)\n│  └─ FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculations (high-level API)\n├─ loaded from (data): FxVanillaOptionTradeCsvPlugin\n└─ embedded in: FxSingleBarrierOption (as underlying)\n```\n\n## Cross-module Dependencies\n\n1. **product → pricer**: Pricer classes depend on Resolved* types from product\n2. **pricer → measure**: Measure classes instantiate and use pricer classes\n3. **measure → measure**: FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction registers requirements and delegates to FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations\n4. **loader → product**: CSV plugin instantiates FxVanillaOptionTrade from CSV data\n5. **product → product**: FxSingleBarrierOption embeds and delegates to FxVanillaOption\n\nThis architecture provides a clean separation of concerns: domain modeling (product), pricing algorithms (pricer), risk calculation framework (measure), and data integration (loader)."
}

